official_title: The Impact of Cigarillo Warnings on Purchasing and Smoking Behaviors Among Young Adult Cigarillo Users, Aim 2 Survey
inclusion_criteria:
* Current cigarillo user-used cigarillos at least one time per week in the past month
* Recruited through Qualtrics Research Services
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must have minimum age of 21 Years
Must have maximum age of 35 Years
exclusion_criteria:
* Not recruited through Qualtrics Research Services
* Non-English speaking
